{"tid":839401,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人千其唔好病","createTime":"2018-09-28T02:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T14:16:22.000Z","uid":36670,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"35a99dea99fd7f42537069f14245476e541bb00e","tid":839401,"uid":36670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:26:08.000Z","msg":"小弟之前去急症，做手術都係去公立醫院<br />\n又迫又多人無wifi無差電，個個醫護都打扙燥底咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到今次帶母親大人去睇專科，見到公立要排成年已經不了<br />\n就帶左佢去私院<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌，地方又大，個門面靚到呢，成間酒店咁撚樣<br />\n琴晚book今日有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個個姑娘笑到五萬咁口<br />\n又有水又有wifi<br />\n<br />\n不過一見到張單真係小弟大半日人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街，窮人真係唔好病<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2181cb53788f11a0575f6d1e1a5ae0f80071f94a","tid":839401,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:27:46.000Z","msg":"次次去專科都排足1粒半鐘，睇就睇果幾分鐘。<br />\n唔係立即死嘅都hea你走，一係叫你自己返黎拎藥食就算。<br />\n慣啦，鬼叫你窮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665745829ca71fd67db2b8dcf4762490bff5663d","tid":839401,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"幾錢？睇咩病？邊間院？"},{"pid":"c98c6bb8e24f7cffad1c45ea7927a8840d69965e","tid":839401,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"大半日人工? 係你搵得多, 定睇私家其實好平?"},{"pid":"7b7d5abdae30a411de2d24c29b2d68ece0afb195","tid":839401,"uid":28076,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T02:30:43.000Z","msg":"上次老母去私家照胃鏡腸鏡<br />\n住一晚埋單都兩皮幾野<br />\n無保險既話真係肉都赤埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d777540778dd3d90d20416a37fe98f0d4a25a726","tid":839401,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"218